    <h1 class="mb-6">AI Search Explained</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Practical insights on AI search visibility. Each episode answers one question clearly.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16">
      <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/ai-search-explained-by-rank4ai/id1877874966" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card text-center">
